OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40320
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1781021473
OL,3,CAbusive partner of judge's daughter
OL,4,Cjailed for life for her murder
OL,6,FShe added: "I will never understand
OL,7,Fwhy Clifton George felt such contempt
OL,8,Fand hatred towards someone I loved so
OL,9,Fmuch."
OL,11,FGeorge, a qualified electrician who
OL,12,Fworked on projects including Crossrail
OL,13,Fand the Northern Line extension,
OL,14,Fstared straight ahead from the dock as
OL,15,FMs Rook's family read out their victim
OL,16,Fimpact statements.
OL,26,@nD@LOUqD@FO]
