OL,3,CAbusive partner of judge's daughter
OL,4,Cjailed for life for her murder
OL,6,FThe trial heard he was the victim of
OL,7,Fviolent abuse at the hands of his
OL,8,Fmother when he was a child, leading to
OL,9,Fhim being taken into care. George also
OL,10,Ftold the court that as a youngster he
OL,11,Fwas traumatised by finding his infant
OL,12,Fsister death in her cot.
OL,14,FHis barrister, Mathew Sherratt KC,
OL,15,Ftold the court: "He understands this
OL,16,Fis a terrible thing he has done."
OL,26,@wD@QOUxD@aO]
