OL,3,CAbusive partner of judge's daughter
OL,4,Cjailed for life for her murder
OL,6,FGeorge pleaded guilty before the trial
OL,7,Fto manslaughter and arson being
OL,8,Freckless as to whether life was
OL,9,Fendangered. The jury convicted him
OL,10,Funanimously of murder.
